-- LG Elec aims for $13 billion in North America sales in '08
-- 
-- Mon Jan 7, 2008 7:04pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/01/08/us-show-lgelectronics-idUSSEW00022220080108

 

 LAS VEGAS  (Reuters) - South Korea's LG Electronics ( 066570.KS ) on Monday said it was aiming to post $13 billion in sales in North America in 2008, up 13 percent from $11.5 billion in 2007. 

 LG Electronics made the announcement at the Consumer Electronics Show in Las Vegas. (Reporting by Marie-France Han; Editing by Sei Chong)